title: Brisbane French Festival: Five signs you might be a Francophile
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › Brisbane French Festival: Five signs ... Brisbane French Festival: Five signs you might be a Francophile 4 hrs ago Read more: Sydney Morning Herald 
As Brisbane enjoys a trs French weekend, it's time to celebrate some of the best things the nation that bestowed champagne on the world has brought to the city. The Brisbane French Festival has brought 2000 bottles of champagne and wine, more than 1.3 tonnes of cheese, cabaret, food and a huge serving of French culture to the Queensland capital.
